&gt;  The way I see it, this guy is making public claims and assertions about equimpment I make, and he admits he is only testing (primary tester), that I do not completely agree wiht. I believe I have an obligation to tell my side, and to state once again, as maker of Moon&#39;s &quot;Telephone to the dead&quot;  equipment, which is in fact is one of my boxes, that I say, all are allowed to use it for whatever they want. Moon in fact has no authority whatsoever as a box tester to restrict it&#39;s use to anyone, nor to claim that his contacts are anymore legitimate than anyone else&#39;s. Moon himself announced to the world, twice on Coast to Coast AM,  that I in fact made the boxes, and as the acknowledged creator/maker/inventor of Frank&#39;s box, I say all can use the damn things freely. In additon, I opened it up to all experimentors in an attempt to verify my results, which is in fact an application of scientific method, known as peer review.
&gt;  
&gt;  Moon&#39;s contacts through the box may in fact be real, I don&#39;t know, personaly, he seems like a good guy, and I find these disaggreements troubling, but everyone has their own way using any technology. If you had a cell phone that calls Mars, that would not mean all cell phones can only be used for such contacts, it&#39;s that same with boxes. There may be many levels of spirit, and who is to say which is acceptable, and which is not? I am unwilling to accept any one person&#39;s results as the only results possible. 
